---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility | Su Casa Mexican Restaurant"
  description="Su Casa Mexican Restaurant is committed to digital accessibility. Learn about our efforts to make our website usable for everyone."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
      <p>Our commitment to an inclusive experience</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="accessibility-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>Su Casa Mexican Restaurant is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone and applying the relevant accessibility standards.</p>

        <h2>Measures Taken</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Semantic HTML for screen reader compatibility</li>
          <li>Keyboard navigation support throughout the site</li>
          <li>Skip-to-content link for easy navigation</li>
          <li>Descriptive alt text on all images</li>
          <li>Sufficient color contrast ratios</li>
          <li>Responsive design for all devices and zoom levels</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you encounter any accessibility barriers on our website, please let us know. We welcome your feedback and will do our best to address any issues promptly.</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+18012551042">(801) 255-1042</a></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:scscmo@gmail.com">scscmo@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 6878 S State Street, Midvale, UT 84047</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, #415f84 100%);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .page-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(209, 97, 93, 0.2) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(242, 186, 101, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: var(--color-tertiary);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--color-sand);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .accessibility-content {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0 var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .content-card {
    background: white;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-card h2 {
    color: var(--color-brown-dark);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .content-card h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .content-card p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .content-card ul {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .content-card a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
